9/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</link><description>加沙战争已经过去六周了，对 2021 年 5 月犹太和阿拉伯公民之间骚乱的报复并未实现。这片黑暗中唯一的一丝善意的背后是什么？</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-19/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约市长指责教授在城市校园里营造了针对犹太人的仇恨氛围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</link><description>市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 在曼哈顿中央犹太教堂告诉会众，校园已“成为仇恨的避风港”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列军队公布了加沙 Al-Shifa 医院内人质的录像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</link><description>此外，以色列军方发言人丹尼尔·哈加里表示，被绑架并带入加沙地带的士兵诺亚·马西亚诺先被带到Al-Shifa医院附近的一处藏身处公寓，随后又被带入医院，并在那里被谋杀。病理报告证实</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</guid></item><item><title>将加沙交给多国部队是一个幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</link><description>战争结束后，阿拉伯国家拒绝向加沙派遣军队，而内塔尼亚胡则排除了巴勒斯坦权力机构控制该地区的可能性。但由非阿拉伯多国部队掌权的想法毫无意义</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列外交官呼吁建立国际联盟，其国民被哈马斯扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/ex-israeli-diplomats-call-for-an-intl-coalition-whose-nationals-are-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018b-e915-d36e-a3cb-f9571b900000</link><description>该组织的代表和以色列退休大使呼吁联合国任命一名人质问题特别代表，要求红十字会在与哈马斯打交道时更加自信</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:57:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/ex-israeli-diplomats-call-for-an-intl-coalition-whose-nationals-are-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018b-e915-d36e-a3cb-f9571b900000</guid></item><item><title>美国相信内塔尼亚胡最终将支持控制加沙的巴勒斯坦权力机构</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-believes-netanyahu-will-eventually-support-palestinian-authority-controlling-gaza/0000018b-e88a-d6b8-a5ab-ecea67b10000</link><description>美国官员认为，如果巴勒斯坦权力机构同意停止在国际机构中针对以色列的行动，并结束其在以色列监狱中为被定罪的杀人犯提供极具争议的支付制度，那么耶路撒冷对巴勒斯坦权力机构的态度将会软化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-believes-netanyahu-will-eventually-support-palestinian-authority-controlling-gaza/0000018b-e88a-d6b8-a5ab-ecea67b10000</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促以色列推迟对加沙南部的袭击，直到北部流离失所的巴勒斯坦人得到解决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presses-to-delay-south-gaza-strikes-until-displaced-palestinians-are-accounted-for/0000018b-e8bd-d6b8-a5ab-ecfff6b10000</link><description>国家安全顾问乔恩·费纳表示，人们“真正担心”以色列将行动转移到南部，在以色列的敦促下，那里有数十万人逃离</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presses-to-delay-south-gaza-strikes-until-displaced-palestinians-are-accounted-for/0000018b-e8bd-d6b8-a5ab-ecfff6b10000</guid></item><item><title>史前澳大利亚人将野狗与家人一起埋葬在空中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-19/ty-article/prehistoric-australians-buried-their-dingoes-in-the-sky-with-people/0000018b-e82d-d570-a7cf-fa7d9be60000</link><description>澳大利亚原住民终生饲养野狗，可能是几代人，这与该岛殖民时代野生小狗袭击的报道形成鲜明对比</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 16:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-19/ty-article/prehistoric-australians-buried-their-dingoes-in-the-sky-with-people/0000018b-e82d-d570-a7cf-fa7d9be60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的福音派恋情无助于削弱美国对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-dont-support-israel-netanyahus-affair-with-evangelicals-isnt-helping/0000018b-e7c1-d05f-a5eb-e7e15af30000</link><description>随着年轻的美国选民越来越倾向于支持巴勒斯坦人而不是以色列，一个群体仍然坚定地支持犹太国家 — — 这只会加剧以色列和民主党之间的分裂</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 16:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-dont-support-israel-netanyahus-affair-with-evangelicals-isnt-helping/0000018b-e7c1-d05f-a5eb-e7e15af30000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大性侵犯中心主任因质疑哈马斯强奸以色列妇女的说法而被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadian-sexual-assault-center-fired-for-questioning-accounts-of-hamas-rapes/0000018b-e7f8-d05f-a5eb-e7f8d6c80000</link><description>阿尔伯塔大学性侵犯中心主任萨曼莎·皮尔森签署了一封信，提到“反复且未经证实的指控巴勒斯坦人犯有性暴力罪”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 15:25:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadian-sexual-assault-center-fired-for-questioning-accounts-of-hamas-rapes/0000018b-e7f8-d05f-a5eb-e7f8d6c80000</guid></item><item><title>东耶路撒冷记者因涉嫌煽动和鼓励恐怖主义而被捕</title><link>http